						<div class="postbody">Hello, I have some questions regarding how the DMC works before it is started. I have the APU registers all set to 0 on startup. Since it is 0, the rate index in $4010 is 428 for NTSC, 398 for PAL on startup? If you do not enable sample playing in reg $4015 bit 4, the DMC timer should still run, and output a clock when the timer is 0? What other units should also run when the DMC playback is disabled? IE, does the output unit run, sending 0 to the mixer?</div>

